  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVolumeReader

    public class DocWordVolumeReader
extends AbstractWordVolumeReader
    DocWordVolumeReader reads a list of treatments from a by the previous charaparser version termed Type 1 input format. This is a description in Microsoft Word format. The DocWordVolumeReader expects the "WordVolumeReader_Sourcefile" to point to the .DOC(X) file contained in the word file
